Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追迹封锁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(344,360)\fs21}Route Disturb
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧丽安娜·汤姆森的外号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得这没人情味的作法  好像在哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她是欧丽安娜  也应该不可能有那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  史提尔  我和你的想法一致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就不是魔术师了  而是魔导师了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要塞进有关魔术的相关知识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些知识就能不经由术者的意志  作为单独魔法阵启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是魔道书的原典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  根据情况制作魔道书那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是原典  也应该只是草书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有原典的效果  不久就会毁坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是「速记原典」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么究竟该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要把自动迎击术式破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让史提尔可以再次使用魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要是在破坏的过程中  目标跑到探索范围以外了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她有逃出去的自信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她还会特意搞一个迎击术式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提尔  什么魔术都好  随便用一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「占术圆阵」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是还没有任何人的魔力通过的未使用魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能对迎击魔术的魔力有所反应而起动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆算魔力源头的方向和距离
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  土御门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用这个的话  史提尔就要再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说过这样的话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不能找出「速记原典」的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(384,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要不停地试下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像忘了一件事  我来好好告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是场性命攸关的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家或世界可能因其结果而倾覆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装熟人  上条当麻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就能解决一切问题  那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的  无论发生什么都要找到迎击术式的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保茵蒂克丝在学园都市里的生活  这就是你的条件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上条当麻  我对你现在在这个地方很有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不在那个孩子身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是因为这个让那个孩子不开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就全部是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得换好衣服  想让当麻瞧瞧的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就随便跑到其它地方去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小修女  不要这么沮丧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小上条肯定有什么难言之隐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上条当麻那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微没注意  人就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小吹寄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在大庭广众下干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是轻微的精神错乱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就使用辣椒粉等刺激物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把思考转移到表层…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事  小吹寄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻他到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占术圆阵有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿上  你有地图喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  手机上有GPS地图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我自己来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御门！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么能那么冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为史提尔是为了谁受的伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是专业的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有做好应付术式攻击的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御门…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占术圆阵能对散发在空中的术式的魔力产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而找出距离与方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么方便的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不用魔力就能发动得起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能够更好地使用魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提尔也不至于变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认  所以随你怎么怨恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我一定会把速记原典找出来破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把欧丽安娜抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定会亲手粉碎这次刺突杭剑的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(437,360)\fs21}Stab Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上  给我地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道西北三百零二米处都有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速记原典一定在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(297,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是初中？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21\fad(100,100)}离初中丢球比赛开始还有十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是赛场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开始已经没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看客和摄像机都已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能悄无声息地行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办啊  也不能就这样放着不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能假装成选手混进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当真想这么干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混进初中生里面也太强人所…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招迎击术式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有向其他人攻击的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么是世界上最简单的魔术仪式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是触摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是不懂魔术的普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过触摸  也有发动迎击术式的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有作为魔术师的防御力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会非常危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出现受害者之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把迎击术式解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来要比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这副打扮出场果然是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且还有录像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有能换的运动服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在活动室里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快点去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我确认一下ID吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能把手擦干净再按啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途参加可是不允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮混进比赛有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常情况保健室里是有能换的衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的比赛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南川中学选拔出来的两百人对阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台中学选拔出来的二十人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢球比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们身上散发出失败的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭死了臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里干什么啊  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  常盘台中学？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有很多很可怕的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要注意流弹哦  阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这里布置有速记原典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是那些篮子很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有从外面借来的篮子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搬进这里之前就能够进行术式设置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会对球篮进行逐一调查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于阿上你  在找到速记原典后就是你的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别退缩  要冲进去了阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这根  阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一根
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上  这根也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上  踩到我的背上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么想让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承担惩罚游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到危险的话就没意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由待会我会详细说明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快点离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  你突然说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  为什么你会在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我详细解释一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂  什么也别说快到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便没有你救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你要对我说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种程度的比赛里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着这么担心我的安危…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  别突然说那么奇怪的事情吓唬别人好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话  不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么难受吗  御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是发烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土御门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的球篮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上条当麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还慌慌张张地跑了  怎么又会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹寄！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去拍一下吹寄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去身体会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹寄  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹寄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧丽安娜·汤姆森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这是你的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但让无辜的人卷进来还丝毫没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那可笑的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎到瓦砾无存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹寄倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史提尔  还有土御门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这场争端的原因是刺突杭剑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(462,360)\fs21}Stab Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就一定要毁掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  速记原典
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(389,360)\fs21}Short Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学与魔术交织之时  故事便拉开序幕


